WEBVTT

00:05.555 --> 00:07.924
He's big, and he is powerful.

00:07.925 --> 00:10.693
He knows that there's people here.

00:10.693 --> 00:12.862
I was immediately freaked out.

00:12.863 --> 00:15.263
It is mean.

00:16.133 --> 00:17.566
Pure hatred and anger.

00:17.567 --> 00:19.969
It scared the living crap out of me.

00:19.970 --> 00:22.505
It has bad intentions.

00:22.506 --> 00:24.908
He was diagnosed with psychosis.

00:24.909 --> 00:27.143
- That's no way to live.
- No.

00:27.144 --> 00:30.211
- Are they dangerous?
- Yes, they are.

00:30.212 --> 00:32.852
They're cursed.

00:33.784 --> 00:35.963
They're being watched.

00:35.964 --> 00:38.988
My name is Amy Allan.

00:38.989 --> 00:41.190
This thing likes death.

00:41.191 --> 00:42.809
I see dead people.

00:42.810 --> 00:44.560
This thing's, like, a monster.

00:44.561 --> 00:46.595
I speak to dead people.

00:46.596 --> 00:48.282
And he's pissed off now.

00:48.283 --> 00:49.676
And they speak to me.

00:49.677 --> 00:51.403
His head was cracked.

00:51.404 --> 00:54.904
But there's only one way to
know if my findings are real.

00:54.905 --> 00:56.395
This guy was murdered.

00:56.396 --> 00:57.893
I rely on my partner.

00:57.894 --> 00:59.306
I'm Steve Di Schiavi.

00:59.307 --> 01:01.165
I'm a retired New York
City homicide Detective.

01:01.166 --> 01:03.879
I cannot help you unless
I know the whole story.

01:03.880 --> 01:07.216
And I know every person,
every house has secrets.

01:07.217 --> 01:08.526
You saw her?

01:08.527 --> 01:09.885
It's my job to reveal them.

01:09.886 --> 01:10.954
Why would you stay here?

01:10.955 --> 01:13.244
But Steve and I never speak...

01:13.245 --> 01:15.325
We never communicate
during an investigation.

01:15.326 --> 01:16.692
Until the very end.

01:16.693 --> 01:18.527
Stop it.

01:18.528 --> 01:20.359
We uncover if it's safe for you to stay...

01:20.360 --> 01:22.939
I want to know the truth. I
want to know what's happening.

01:22.940 --> 01:24.367
Or time to get out.

01:24.368 --> 01:29.048
I told you there were ghosts in this house.

